   "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
   "body" : "There are still many functional tests that perform conversions from a message object to a hex-string (serialization) and vice-versa (deserialization) manually. This PR identifies all those instances and replaces them with the helpers `FromHex` and `ToHex`, respectively, that have been introduced for exactly that purpose.\r\n\r\nInstances were found via\r\n* `git grep \"serialize().hex()\"`\r\n* `git grep \"deserialize.*BytesIO\"`\r\n\r\nand some of them manually, when it were not one-liners.",
